page_title: 'Quickstart: Use the OpenAI Service image generation Go SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI image generation using the Go SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free* Go 1.8+- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the East US region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.
